Run reset.sh by typing the following command:
sh reset.sh 
It will create the required database directories and files

run the server in one terminal
run the client in other

first sign up and create one admin account. 
it will ask for a secret for admin account. the secret is "root"

now login into admin account and add trains

create a customer and login to book ticket


As the functions of agent and customer are same .. the login part of agent has to be edited/ linked
the difference between in customer and agent is:
customer-> Single Access
agent -> Multiple Access

admin - id/password -> 2/admin123
client - id/password -> 2/c1

